    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_zs.00230.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden<ptr target="loc.08107_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1890-05-06">PM May 6 '90</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Have not written much lately because I expect to see you soon &amp; I have had four 
              days of this siege of grip viciously 
                departing (I hope departing)&#8212;But am decidedly easier to-day&#8212;am weaker than ever&#8212;my 
                thoughts clear enough I suppose, but legs &amp; spine weak, weak&#8212;appetite (wh' was quite gone) 
                returning wet &amp; dark weather</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>&#8212;Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
